source: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_SEQ_00<tab>Holepix is ready to let slip the dogs of war.

TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_SEQ_01<tab>Holepix believes his kin will not taste true peace until Idyllshire impresses their strength upon the Illuminati. To that end, he bids you go to the Arkhitekton and slay any six Illuminati goblins─be they brandishers, tinkerers, sharpshooters, or gliders.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_SEQ_01<tab>Holepix vous a demandé de vaincre des Gobelins de la Main indigo pour les éloigner du hameau. Allez à L'Arkhitékton et terrassez six Gobelins au choix parmi les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E0E0302 /var>, les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E0F0302 /var>, les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E100302 /var> ou les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E110302 /var>.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_SEQ_02<tab>You slay six members of the Illuminati. Return now to Holepix, and see if this sates his bloodlust.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez vaincu les Gobelins de la Main indigo. Faites un rapport à Holepix.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_SEQ_03<tab>Holepix is happy with the message of dominance you have sent the Illuminati. However, he fears that the enemies of Idyllshire will yet rally, and attack again from the shadows. Hence, he vows to increase the guard, to keep his kith and kin safe.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_SEQ_03<tab>Vous avez rapporté vos résultats à Holepix. Celui-ci semble convaincu que la Main indigo mijote des choses plus que louches...

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_000Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Gobbiekin of Holepix speak of peace. But no can be peace without war, not while Illuminati try to steal territory of Idyllshire!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_000<tab>Pssshh... L'heure a sonné<var 1D /var>! Envoyons les signaux de fumée, lançons l'offensive<var 1D /var>! C'est le moment de taper sur les doigts de la Main indigo<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_001<tab>Now is not time to put away fighty-tool! Now is time to raise it! Uplander, take heads from six of hated foes for Holepix! Show Illuminati that Idyllshire is not having fear of them or their Arkhitekton!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_001<tab>Le combat aura lieu à L'Arkhitékton<var 1D /var>! L'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> veut bien vaincre six méchants Gobelins pour aider<var 1D /var>?
TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_010<tab>Le combat aura lieu à L'Arkhitékton<var 1D /var>! L'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> veut bien vaincre six méchants Gobelins pour aider<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_020<tab>Shkohhh... Hah! Uplander crush braincases of Illuminati like eggs! Idyllshire wins today!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_020<tab>Pssshh... Bravo, brave aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var><var 1D /var>! Holepix a tout vu<var 1D /var>! Les gentils Gobelins du bivouac auront l'avantage, grâce à l'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_021<tab>But war is not over. Illuminati still have lustyeyes for land of Idyllshire. They still take knowings with cruelness, keep them with fighty-tools.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_021La Main indigo cherche le savoir par tous les moyens, ils sont mauvais!
La Main indigo pratique le culte du secret, ils sont égoïstes! Il faut les punir!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_022<tab>Illuminati will attack with tricksy plans and secret schemes. Holepix will make sure to double─no, <var 1A 02 /var>triple<var 1A 01 /var> guards! Idyllshire will not lose war! Never!
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ808_01938_HOLEPIX_000_022Ils mijotent toujours quelque chose de louche!
Il faut les surveiller et leur donner un bon coup sur les doigts!
